{"threadmark": "Chapter 6 and Interrupt: Division", "post-id": "72869744", "base-thread": "the-last-angel-the-hungry-stars", "url": "https://forums.spacebattles.com/threads/the-last-angel-the-hungry-stars.868549/reader//#post-72869744", "lines": ["Merry Christmas (or a happy December 25th) to everyone!", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.750rem\">My <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/user?u=3199716\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Patreon</a>/</span>", "<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/user?u=3199716\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Patreon</a>", "<a href=\"https://www.subscribestar.com/proximal-flame\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link link--external\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.750rem\">subscribestar</span></a>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.750rem\">subscribestar</span>", "<b><span style=\"font-size: 1.375rem\">Chapter 6</span></b>", "<span style=\"font-size: 1.375rem\">Chapter 6</span>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Reginn</i>", "<i>Lakhesis\u2019s</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>This is not solely our war. We fight to avenge the lost, and that includes so much more than our own kin. You need to understand that, little one.</i>", "<i>Redemption of Sol</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Reginn</i>", "<i>were</i>", "<i>perhaps</i>", "<i>Maybe</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>didn\u2019t</i>", "<i>Reginn</i>", "<i>anj</i>", "<i>anj</i>", "<i>Exsanguinator</i>", "<i>Exterminatrix</i>", "<i>old</i>", "<i>-illth,</i>", "<i>anj</i>", "<i>-illth</i>", "<i>illth</i>", "<i>illth</i>", "<i>illth</i>", "<i>-anj</i>", "<i>anj</i>", "<i>-illth</i>", "<i>-illth</i>", "<i>never trust a snake when you can\u2019t see her teeth.</i>", "<i>Thorncastle</i>", "<i>Slaughterstar</i>", "<i>Slaughterstar</i>", "<i>Purgebringer</i>", "<i>Exansanguinator</i>", "<i>how</i>", "<i>developments</i>", "<i>And then tomorrow, you\u2019d better tell me what this new \u2018development\u2019 is, or my hospitality is going to become strained.</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>LAKHESIS<br>\nSCX-0002</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Clotho</i>", "<i>Atropos</i>", "<i>About how you killed four hundred thousand people for no reason other than you wanted to.</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Besides, Red isn\u2019t infallible. She could be wrong.</i>", "<i>And we need to know if she\u2019s going to go insane.</i>", "<i>Kavili visarii</i>", "<i>Nenem ariashtu</i>", "<i>Hopefully</i>", "<b><span style=\"font-size: 1.375rem\">Interrupt: Division</span></b>", "<span style=\"font-size: 1.375rem\">Interrupt: Division</span>", "<i> Wandering Paul</i>", "<i>agnostic</i>", "<i> quasi</i>", "<i>ever</i>", "<i>Promise me, Miguel</i>", "<i>I wonder why a man who used to be an </i>", "<i> was talking about doing geological studies after he\u2019d gone \u2018round the bed? No, gotta be something holy and visionary. A last benediction and gift of wisdom from the Prophet, right? </i>", "<i>And the Cult of Siegland keeps on growing</i>"]}
