, "<i>\u2018Cerulean Two\u2019 is bit of a mouthful to say every time and I don\u2019t want to call you by a number. How do you like \u2018Leah\u2019?</i>", "<i>Acceptable</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Rome wasn\u2019t built in a day,</i>", "<i> Hekate</i>", "<i>Hekate</i>", "<i>Athena</i>", "<i>Nemesis-</i>", "<i>The things fate gives us...</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Nemesis</i>", "<i>Maybe tomorrow</i>", "<i>Maybe tomorrow.</i>", "<i>Lakhesis</i>", "<i>Terror, the human form divine</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>Stay silent. Stay safe.</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>explore</i>", "<i>Vegvisir </i>", "<i>What are we passing by?</i>", "<i>Vegivisir</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>L\u00e1sabrj\u00f3tur</i>", "<i>Kong\u014d</i>", "<i> Especially </i>", "<i>Nothing except...</i>", "<i>Case in point</i>", "<i>We didn\u2019t know what was so close to us.</i>", "<i>Lazaretto</i>", "<i>Vegvisir</i>", "<i>L\u00e1sabrj\u00f3tur</i>", "<i>did</i>", "<i>Don\u2019t listen to the songs.</i>", "<i>Don\u2019t listen to the songs.</i>", "<i>Which means these can\u2019t be here, can they? </i>", "<i>Aramburu, Masako, Tamerlane </i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Sammuram\u0101t</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Telepathy, if it were made with radio waves</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Zenobia</i>", "<i>Zenobia</i>", "<i>Zenobia</i>", "<i>Though I know full well she has other motives.</i>", "<i>Zenobia</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>i</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>Bathory\u2019s </i>", "<i>Bathory</i>", "<i>yes</i>", "<i>Life-thief</i>", "<i>opamp</i>", "<i>But.</i>", "<i>better</i>", "<i>Life-thief</i>", "<i> kaoa</i>", "<i>Scars</i>", "<i>Splinters</i>", "<i>Slashes</i>", "<i>Skinweaver</i>", "<i> akla nah</i>", "<i>\u2019</i>", "<i>Life-thief</i>", "<i>Life-thief</i>", "<i>Not that it will make any difference in the end</i>", "<i>Cold Hammer</i>", "<i>Life-thief</i>", "<i>Here</i>", "<i>and that\u2019s where you\u2019ll die.</i>"]}
